  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9c\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bb9\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b9f \u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 - \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A special discussion led by Mahinda bringing together the members of Podujana Peramuna - Sagara Kariyavasam",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Podujana Peramuna will give its full support to the President Ranil Wickremesinghe-led government.",
        "Sagara Kariyawasam, Secretary General of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna said that we have decided to bring together the members of Podujana Peramuna and carry out special talks under the leadership of former Prime Minister Mahinda Rajapaksa.",
        "In the situation where the economic crisis has intensified in the country, we have supported the formation of the government under the leadership of President Ranil Wickremesinghe so that political factors should not be given priority.",
        "A few members of Podujana Peramuna have refrained from supporting President Ranil Wickremesinghe based on their personal animosity.",
        "We have supported President Ranil Wickremesinghe so that political factors should not be prioritized when the economic crisis has intensified.",
        "It cannot be assumed that everyone's views are unanimous in all cases.",
        "Therefore, we have decided to bring together all the members and carry out a special discussion under the leadership of former Prime Minister Party leader Mahinda Rajapaksa.",
        "The narrow political agenda of the 10 political parties that claim to be independent in Parliament has undermined the entire political structure.",
        "He said that we will soon make it public with evidence that the protests have taken place due to political manipulation and are taking place."
      ],
